 smell\n|on it like a car bonnet\n|race car driver\n|stop the car|aerocar|aircar|anticar|automocar|caraholic|carbarn|carbeam|carborne|carcoat|carcoon|carden|carfie|carfleet|carful|cargasm|carhop|carhouse|carjack|carjacking|carless|carlike|carline|carloading|carlot|Carmageddon|carmaker|carmaking|carmate|carnap|carnapper|carnapping|carness|carplane|carpool|carpooler|carport|carshare|carsick|carside|carspiel|carsploitation|cartop|cartopper|carwasher|carwashing|Comcar|cruck|cyclecar|decar|ecocar|econocar|forecar|gyrocar|handcar|housecar|hovercar|hydrocar|hypercar|incar|jetcar|McCar|microcar|minecar|minicar|multicar|nanocar|outcar|podcar|robocar|sidecar|supercar|Swasticar|tramcar|tricar|turbocar|undercar|car safety seat|chemical car|log car|rent-a-car|read the car}}\n\n=====Related terms=====\n* {{l|en|carriage}}\n* {{l|en|chariot}}\n\n=====Descendants=====\n* {{desc|fr|car|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ru|кар|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|sa|कारयान|der=1}}\n* {{desc|ta|கார்|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ja|カー|tr=kā|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ko|카|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|hi|कार|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ur|کار|bor=1}}\n\n=====Translations=====\n{{trans-top|automobile, a vehicle steered by a driver}}\n{{multitrans|data=\n* Afrikaans: {{tt+|af|kar}}, {{tt|af|motorkar}}\n* Ahom: {{t-needed|aho}}\n* Ahtna: {{t|aht|ghalbesi}}, {{t|aht|łoodaxi}}, {{t|aht|natetdaxa}}\n* Alabama: {{tt|akz|mobìlka}}\n* Albanian: {{tt+|sq|makinë}}, {{tt+|sq|automobil|m}}, {{tt|sq|kerr|m}} {{qualifier|Kosovo}}, {{tt|sq|rrabë}} {{qualifier|Macedonia}}\n* Altai:\n*: Southern Altai: {{t|alt|машина}}, {{t|alt|автомобиль}}, {{t|alt|кӧлӱк}}\n* Ambonese Malay: {{tt|abs|oto}}\n* Amharic: {{tt|am|መኪና}}\n* Apache:\n*: Western Apache: {{tt|apw|náłbill}}\n* Arabic: {{tt+|ar|سَيَّارَة|f}}\n*: Chadian Arabic: {{t|shu|وتير|tr=watīr}}\n*: Egyptian Arabic: {{tt|arz|عَرَبِيَّة|f|tr=ʕarabiyya}}, {{tt|arz|سَيَّارَة|f}}\n*: Gulf Arabic: {{tt|afb|سيارة|f|tr=sayyāra}}\n*: Hijazi Arabic: {{tt|acw|سَيَّارَة|f|tr=sayyāra}}\n*: Juba Arabic: {{t|pga|arabiiya}}\n*: Moroccan Arabic: {{